column5: It's been reported that Willie Nelson has been killed. Apparently he was playing on the road again!!!
Sir Crank,  You got me good on that one, Im still roflmao.  Thanks for a great laugh, great way to start the day off.  lol lol.
Don't scare me like that. He's supposed to be playing a tune or two at my funeral.
Don't scare me like that. He's supposed to be playing a tune or two at my funeral.  He,ll be gone long before you go me brudder.   It did have me googeling to find out though. LOL
Willie's in his 80s and by all accounts has lived pretty hard, I reckon he is already on borrowed time...............
